detailedDescription.articleBody:
Madhabi Mukherjee née Chakraborty [মাধবী মুখার্জী ] is an Indian actress who has won the National Film Award for Best Actress for the Bengali film Dibratrir Kabya. She has acted in some of the most critically acclaimed films in Bengali cinema.
Her major role was the title role of Charu in Satyajit Ray's masterpiece Charulata.
